          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2014-05-09</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>European Union Religious Freedom Act - Amends the International Religious Freedom Act of 1998 to include among Congress's finding with respect to the forms of government-sponsored or government-tolerated violations of religious freedom prohibitions against: (1) homeschooling, (2) religious methods of meat production, (3) circumcision, and (4) wearing religious garb. </p>]]></text>
